RN, White GH, Cain M, McCarthy PJ, Booth J "Hyperkalemia in the elderly." Clin Chem 30 (1984): 1409-12[25] "Product Information. Diovan (valsartan)." Novartis Pharmaceuticals, East Hanover, NJ.[26] "Product Information. Cozaar (losartan)." Merck & Co, Inc, West Point, PA.', 'Amlodipine, Sacubitril, Hydrochlorothiazide', NULL, 1767369485);
