e, Cefuroxime, Secnidazole, Cefixime, Amikacin, Rifamycin, Kanamycin, Ampicillin, More', 'Alvimopan, Sorbitol, Magnesium sulfate, Methylnaltrexone, Magnesium oxide, Plecanatide, Lubiprostone, Methylcellulose, Prucalopride, Linaclotide, Naloxone', 1767369485);
